title: Cashmere Arm Sox—Violet
description:
This cozy cashmere Arm Sox has two openings for your fingers and thumb and a knitted sleeve that goes all the way up to your elbow. Perfect to wear with a 3/4-sleeve coat, or a sweater when you want extra warmth and a layered look. For men and women. 100% cashmere. One size.

Color:  Violet Purple

3.25 in. W x 16.25 in. L
